bug.short_desc: java.io.FileNotFoundException results in search form to be displayed in results

long_desc.thetext: It can happen that file is removed from a repository and this change is done on disk before indexer runs. In this time window, when a user search hits the file which has been removed from the repository an error message is displayed inside the results in a weird fashion.
Attaching a screenshot, pardon the redacted version; I believe it illustrates the problem sufficiently.
